[resource]
script = ExtResource("1_1leur")
release_version = "v1.2.4"
notes = "[TITLE]Items
Increased the effects of the Anti-Cog Control Hat
Slightly buffed the positive rolls for Philosopher's Stone
Reorganized the Item Pools for what is definitely the last final and for real time
  Bronze Chests now spawn naturally
  Silver Chests now hold Accessories/Pocket Pranks
  Gold Chests are notably rarer and hold better Items
[TITLE]Characters
Mystery Toon's random Accessory and Pocket Prank are now unaffected by Item rarity
[TITLE]Bosses
Added an indicator for your current position when respawning in The Liquidator boss fight
[TITLE]Title Screen
Mystery Toon's look can now be instantly refreshed by clicking their tab again once they have landed on the ground
[TITLE]Facilities
Floor Reward Items will now be obtained via a special chest found when completing a boss
Mole Stomp now displays instructions when the game starts
Improved the feel of the bellows spring collisions in the Molten Mint
[TITLE]Cog Creator
Custom Cogs now support custom department emblems (only through manual editing, the attribute name is \"custom_emblem_tex\")
[TITLE]Tweaks
Starting Accessories are now displayed on the Toon during the falling cutscene
[TITLE]Bugfixes
Fixed a crash that occurred if you managed to use Big Foghorn twice in the same room
Fixed an issue where the Wheelhouse Proxy Cog effect would not activate properly
Calculator has been added to the \"everything\" Item Pool"
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://d1j0hh6tsgy0r"
